title: 2014 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 10)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
2014 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

This thing is jam packed with some namers today.  To point out a few, there is Jesus Culture, Jars of Clay, PlanetShakers, and Peter Furler.  There is Hillsong, Donnie McClurkin, James Fortune And FIYA (thanks bdurden11), and Memphis May Fire.  There is Sleeping At Last, Future Of Forestry, The Royal Royal, and even a couple of singles from the newly formed PawnShop Kings that you've got to make sure you take a moment to check out.

That being said, I hope there's a little something for everyone in today's bundle.  It is my continued prayer that one of these songs, perhaps even a mere lyric within, draws you nearer to the Father.

REGGAE: Addis Pablo.  SINGER-SONGWRITER: Brothers, Worship Outreach.  PRAISE & WORSHIP: CentricWorship, Hillsong, Jesus Culture, Michael Ketterer.  CONTEMPORARY: Chayah Miranda, PlanetShakers.  R&B: Chelle.  HIP-HOP/RAP: Chozen, Ghost And Rocdwell, Jay Is Real, Righteouz Knight, Sammy Sayso, True Wordz.  BLUES: Clint Morgan And The Lost Cause.  ROCK: Devin Williams, Jars of Clay, Peter Furler, The Royal Royal, Satellites And Sirens.  GOSPEL: Donnie McClurkin, James Fortune And FIYA.  ALTERNATIVE: Future Of Forestry, Scarlet White, Sleeping At Last.  INSTRUMENTAL: John Zorn.  HARDCORE/METAL: Memphis May Fire.  INDIE: PawnShop Kings.

We have now shared 389 releases amongst ourselves this year.

There are 37 titles being shared in this 10th bundle today, including...
